<HEADLINE>
<P>
SERVICE SET FOR JIM BACKUS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A public memorial service for actor-comedian Jim Backus, voice of the 
quarrelsome "Mr. Magoo" throughout that animated figure's lengthy career and a 
star of the old "Gilligan's Island" TV series, will be held Wednesday at noon 
at the Screen Directors Guild, 7920 Sunset Blvd. Backus was 76 when he died 
July 3. 
</P>
</TEXT>
