<P>
POLICE MISCONDUCT; DRUNK DRIVING; TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
GREEN, ROLLO; TORRANCE (CA) -- SUITS; TORRANCE POLICE DEPARTMENT; TRIALS 
</P>
