Fibrosis Summer Camp. From left, Joe Marchiano, Bob Crabb, Dr. Ivan Harwood, 
Bob Flanagan and Rocky Gomes. ; Photo, COLOR, Melody Johnson, 8, of Ontario 
plays "guess who" with volunteer Paul Maag, above, while Brian Ernst, 10, leaps 
on a huge beach ball in the swimming pool at the Cystic Fibrosis summer Camp. ; 
Photo, COLOR, Bob Crabb hugs Michael Harper after water fight. ; Photo, COLOR, 
